seo: Webgrind,CVE-2018-12909,任意文件读取漏洞,插件,检测
summary: 该插件用于检测Webgrind应用是否存在CVE-2018-12909任意文件读取漏洞，通过访问特定路径判断是否存在漏洞。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the Webgrind application has the CVE-2018-12909 arbitrary file read vulnerability by accessing a specific path to determine if the vulnerability exists.
